Fifteen of the largest banks choose "Russia"
The conflict in the Association of Russian Banks (ADB) is developing: following Sberbank, VTB, VTB-24, Alfa-bank, Gazprombank, rosagricultural Bank, Binbank and FC "discovery," seven more credit organizations are going to leave this public organization.
Thus, organizations that have withdrawn from the ADB will account for at least 80 per cent of the market.
